                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                    "id": "84c33fea-c4d7-427e-90dd-b5f1e566cf43",
                    "scope": "actor",
                    "scopeId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                    "tagsToAdd": "tippedgarden",
                    "tagsToRemove": null
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "5fc57bbd-8f85-4bd0-abf0-ce3834bae2c5",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we will be discussing the Puffball mushroom. You've seen them growing in the garden. They are the large, tan and white fungi balls that grow without a noticeable stalk.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "586a41e3-e14b-4f8c-90f8-17e095417d31",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "These mushrooms can be found in the shade of oaks or cypress and in caves with fresh water.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "ad511ba2-ec1f-490b-aa38-9f6fa17e114d",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "They have healing properties and are the primary ingredient of many medicines. In an emergency, they can be eaten raw to restore some of your health. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "fa893138-68c8-47af-8c92-c88c8292207f",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "However, since they taste bitter and woody, I don't recommend it. They can even make you sick to your stomach. Then again, in a fight, eating Puffballs might save your life.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "3c3415d5-bb03-4017-b6a6-9922bb09d283",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We'll be taking a close look at them to make sure that you can safely identify the Puffball growing in the wild. Any questions before we start dissecting these mushrooms?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "a940690d-1bbd-4199-840b-a0a135d61b78",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "32482f53-bf11-42a0-ac72-64f5afb3752a",
                            "text": "Say Something Ingratiating About Mushrooms",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "2886c9d5-70a4-4e1b-8b96-fb40f8c2a24c",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "32",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "92205f69-0a71-4c22-8b52-b6c5795891ff",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Since these mushrooms are so useful, would it be better if we don't pick them from the garden? Shouldn't they be left so that they will be available in case of emergency?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "cf92651a-d1bf-4d07-87b3-8fc6d3142d61",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "05465d4f-884c-4799-a95e-df39ddaa4a10",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "That's a good thought, Shawn. However, Puffballs grow very rapidly and they only last for a few days. If you find some in the Tower Garden, feel free to take a few.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "738a6dc4-0478-4e0d-a7bb-fce91692a61d",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I have a large garden on the castle grounds where I grow most of the medicinal plants and fungi used in the Infirmary.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "be82cd7d-bc7d-4338-bb66-01418af937aa",
                            "text": "Ask Something Clever About Puffballs",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "608e71e3-3c88-4fb2-ab7f-6e209985cbf7",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "32",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f629f32d-89db-43f5-9ea0-0d58dd3b20e4",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "Puffballs seem pretty easy to identify. Are there any other mushrooms that can be confused with them?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "7c5cbec5-6a49-4ae0-b632-3b8a69d9a516",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d4b4129a-31e2-46bb-a0ea-02e5321c0e49",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, there are some poisonous mushrooms that look similar to Puffballs when they are immature. That's why we'll be studying the qualities that make Puffballs unique.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "a2100aa5-4c34-44bb-96c7-1bdc949b9ba9",
                            "text": "Say Something Irrelevant",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
