                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "To begin this discussion, I will give you all three Puffballs to study and take with you. These will help you identify Puffballs in the wild and can be eaten to treat injuries during combat or other emergencies.",
